Okay, my position is dreadful to look at, but at this point I'm thinking my opponent's position might even be a bit worse ...and not just visually. Typically, I could kiss people who castle long in inferior positions. By doing so they're just begging me to start a direct pawnstorm attack against their King ...which is what I do here. I would have thought twice about that, though, except for the fact that all Black's pieces are walking on each other's toes while mine, ugly ducklings for the moment, are poised to become graceful swans.
